    "description": "这是一款资源管理游戏，你将指挥一队智能机器人，拯救整个世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/387c8cf12de144f8146b55d676aaa216.poster.avif?t=1763443459\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/387c8cf12de144f8146b55d676aaa216.webm?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/387c8cf12de144f8146b55d676aaa216.mp4?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>想好建筑建造的位置和需要采集的资源，后面的脏活累活就可以交给机器人了。它们会采集资源、建造建筑、装填兵器、战斗，也会响应身边的世界。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/3295bdea93dbab8daceed33136ab0b7d.poster.avif?t=1763443459\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/3295bdea93dbab8daceed33136ab0b7d.webm?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/3295bdea93dbab8daceed33136ab0b7d.mp4?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏没有沙盒世界，你需要在有限的空间建设若干较小的基地。所有基地都会同时运转，也有可能同时遭到敌方袭击，所以务必多加小心。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/fa10ca8ff57e50792cc55315ea505c39.poster.avif?t=1763443459\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/fa10ca8ff57e50792cc55315ea505c39.webm?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/fa10ca8ff57e50792cc55315ea505c39.mp4?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏共有五个区域，每一个的资源和科技各不相同。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/61ed4839e81b5c1378085ae69038d0e8.poster.avif?t=1763443459\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/61ed4839e81b5c1378085ae69038d0e8.webm?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/61ed4839e81b5c1378085ae69038d0e8.mp4?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>黑暗的敌人邪恶狠毒，他们会袭击你的基地，企图摧毁你的反应装置，抢夺你的资源。建造防御设施，装填箭矢弹药，即可击退入侵的敌人。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/0357fc2ae762b70be7d0a1589b229775.poster.avif?t=1763443459\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/0357fc2ae762b70be7d0a1589b229775.webm?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1719240/extras/0357fc2ae762b70be7d0a1589b229775.mp4?t=1763443459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>不断冒险，探索世界，寻找隐蔽的宝藏，参与自动战斗，对抗敌人。这样以来，你就能获得稀有资源，为自己所用。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >点亮光塔，打造自己的军队，解放整个世界</h2>光星球已被黑暗占领。点亮各地的光塔，率领魔像大军驱散黑暗，逐一解放五片区域，渐渐了解这颗星球遭遇了什么。",
